cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it describes the development of machine translation systems for the biomedical translation shared task. Additionally, the use of statistical and neural machine translation toolkits suggests that it may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The inclusion of terminological resources from UMLS indicates that it may also be relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
